revision.text: * [[File:Gengar.png|35px]] Gengar (attacking) vs. [[File:Kangaskhan.png|35px]] Kangaskhan (defending) - Gengar is dual ghost-poison typed and Kangaskhan is mono normal typed. Gengar's ghost type is 0x effective (immune) against Kangaskhan while Gengar's poison type is 1x effective (normal-effective). Thus, Gengar's poison type is the type that is used. Gengar's attack against Kangaskhan is neither increased nor decreased as per the type multiplier of 1 (1x).
